:

1. *Čekam* da vidim šta će da se desi. (I'm waiting to see what will happen.)
2. *Čekala* sam čitavu noć. (I waited the whole night.)
3. *Čekam* da mi se javi. (I'm waiting for them to contact me.)
4. *Čeka* da počne sezona. (They're waiting for the season to start.)
5. *Čekajući* njegov odgovor, bila sam u nedoumici. (Waiting for his answer, I was in doubt.)
6. *Čeka* te sestra. (Your sister is waiting for you.)